metadata.title: ART & ARTIFACT Birds Wind Chime - Hand-Painted Wood and Metal Windbells, Indoor/Outdoor Home and Garden Decor Windchime
features: WOODEN BIRD WIND CHIME - This charming windchime is like having your own little flock of hand-carved, hand-painted birds.
HANDCRAFTED - Suspended from varied lengths of copper-toned metal chain, each colorful 3" wood birdie is perched on a small cone-shaped bell.
DYNAMIC DESIGN - As the bell clappers catch the breeze, they ding softly with a sound as sweet as a bird's song.

DELIGHTFUL HOME DECOR - Displayed on a porch, hung from your favorite tree in the yard or on a shepherd's hook in the garden, this chime is a pretty accent wherever you place it. Wood is lacquered for outdoor use, but chime will weather over time.
THOUGHTFUL GIFT - Perfect for bird lovers and gardeners, this handpainted bird chime makes a beautiful housewarming, birthday or holiday present.
description: This charming windchime is like having your own little flock of hand-carved, hand-painted birds. Suspended from varied lengths of copper-toned metal chain, each colorful 3" wood birdie is perched on a small cone-shaped bell. As the bell clappers catch the breeze, they ding softly with a sound as sweet as a bird's song. At home when hung from the branch of a tree or a shepherd's hook in the garden, it makes an eye-catching and ear-pleasing accent to your outdoor home decor. A great housewarming or birthday gift, it measures 7" diameter, hangs 26". Wooden birds are lacquered for outdoor use, but chime will weather over time.
